{"id":"guide/i18n-common-add-package","title":"Add the localize package","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-add-package.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"add-the-localize-package\" translation-result=\"on\">新增本地化套件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Add the localize package<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要利用 Angular 的本地化功能，請用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 將 <code>@angular/localize</code> 包新增到你的專案中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To take advantage of the localization features of Angular, use the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> to add the <code>@angular/localize</code> package to your project.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要新增 <code>@angular/localize</code> 套件，請使用如下命令來更新專案中的 <code>package.json</code> 和 <code>polyfills.ts</code> 檔案。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To add the <code>@angular/localize</code> package, use the following command to update the <code>package.json</code> and TypeScript configuration files in your project.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"i18n/doc-files/commands.sh\" region=\"add-localize\">\nng add @angular/localize\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">它在 TypeScript 配置檔案中新增 <code>types: [\"@angular/localize\"]</code>，並在 <code>main.ts</code> 檔案頂部新增對 <code>@angular/localize</code> 型別定義的參考。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">It adds <code>types: [\"@angular/localize\"]</code> in the TypeScript configuration files as well as the reference to the type definition of <code>@angular/localize</code> at the top of the <code>main.ts</code> file.</p>\n\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有關 <code>package.json</code> 和 <code>polyfill</code> 套件的更多資訊，請參閱<a href=\"guide/npm-packages\" title=\"Workspace npm dependencies | Angular\">工作區的 npm 依賴項</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For more information about <code>package.json</code> and <code>tsconfig.json</code> files, see <a href=\"guide/npm-packages\" title=\"Workspace npm dependencies | Angular\">Workspace npm dependencies</a> and <a href=\"guide/typescript-configuration\" title=\"TypeScript Configuration | Angular\">TypeScript Configuration</a>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果尚未安裝 <code>@angular/localize</code>，而你試圖建構此專案的本地化版本，<a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 就會報錯。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If <code>@angular/localize</code> is not installed and you try to build a localized version of your project (for example, while using the <code>i18n</code> attributes in templates), the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> will generate an error, which would contain the steps that you can take to enable i18n for your project.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"options\" translation-result=\"on\">選項<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Options<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">選項</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">OPTION</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">說明</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">DESCRIPTION</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">值的型別</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">VALUE TYPE</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">預設值</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">DEFAULT VALUE</nt-wrapper></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>--project</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">專案的名稱。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">The name of the project.</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>string</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>--use-at-runtime</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">如果設定了，則可以在執行時使用 <code><a href=\"api/localize/init/$localize\" class=\"code-anchor\">$localize</a></code>。同時，<code>@angular/localize</code> 也包含在 <code>package.json</code> 的 <code>dependencies</code> 部分，而不是預設的 <code>devDependencies</code>。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">If set, then <code><a href=\"api/localize/init/$localize\" class=\"code-anchor\">$localize</a></code> can be used at runtime. Also <code>@angular/localize</code> gets included in the <code>dependencies</code> section of <code>package.json</code>, rather than <code>devDependencies</code>, which is the default.</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>boolean</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>false</code></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要了解更多可用選項，請參閱 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 中的 <a href=\"cli/add\" title=\"ng add | CLI | Angular\">ng add</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For more available options, see <a href=\"cli/add\" title=\"ng add | CLI | Angular\">ng add</a> in <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What's next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"api/localize\" title=\"$localize | @angular/localize - API | Angular\"><code>@angular/localize</code> API</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">透過 ID 參考語音環境</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">Refer to locales by ID</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：3/10/2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/localize\n - api/localize/init/$localize\n - cli\n - cli/add\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#options\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#下一步呢\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#新增本地化包\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#選項\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/npm-packages\n - guide/typescript-configuration\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-add-package.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}